        <briefdescription>
<para>Processes all deferred components and activates expired ones. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For each entity with DelayedComponentEnabler: 1. Decrements all delay timers by deltaTime 2. Enables components whose timers reach zero 3. Removes activated components from the deferred list</para>
